<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.6.1">
<l>eṅkā ṉumītop patōrmā yamuṇṭē naranā raṇaṉā yulakat taṟanūl</l>
<l>ciṅkā maivirit tavaṉem perumā ṉatuvaṉ ṟiyumceñ cuṭarum nilaṉum</l>
<l>poṅkār kaṭalum poruppum neruppum nerukkip pukapoṉ miṭaṟat taṉaipō</l>
<l>taṅkān tavaṉkāṇ miṉiṉṟāyc ciyarā laḷaiveṇ ṇeyuṇṭāp puṇṭirun tavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, as Nara Nārāyaṇa, propounded the book of virtues</l>
<l rend="indent">so that they do not lapse in this world,</l>
<l>Our great lord who, besides that, compressing the blazing sun, the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">wave-filled seas, mountains, and fire,</l>
<l>Opened his mouth at the time when they entered his golden throat,</l>
<l rend="indent">see, he is the one who was bound,</l>
<l>Having eaten the butter churned by the herder women today.</l>
<l rend="indent">Is there a marvel like this anywhere?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
